Dancing Hitler


Hello, I am Dancing Hitler. I am someone who can provide a few necessary services anonymously over the darkweb. These services will be very useful to you. But before we talk about what I can do, I have a question for you.

What experiences do you want in your lifetime?

Seems like a bullshit question doesn't it? But then again here you are on the deepweb. On my site. If you weren't looking for something we probably wouldn't be talking right now and you wouldn't be enjoying that ridiculous gif which helped me get your attention . If you are 100% content why even try to find someone like me (I am assuming your friends didn't just send you to this site as a joke. If they did haha).

I think we both know that you are not 100% right now. So lets discuss a few things that you want and see if we can work something out. You want greater freedom. Being on Tor attests to that. You want more success and income. Being on my site attests to that. You want more experience and full satisfaction in life. That you're still talking to me attests to that. I think my services can help you.

I offer almost anything you can find on the darkweb. This includes financial products, recreational drugs, counterfeits of all descriptions and business opportunities, as well as a whole variety of items that simply resist categorisation. For the most part I don't produce these goods by myself. I am a reseller. I have a lot of contacts. I can probably find what it is you are looking for and sell it to you.

My services can help you reach a better place. When you have a variety of new avenues to make money you can be more discerning about what you do and who you work with. When you have better profits for less effort you can choose when you want to work. When you have more money and financial security you can enjoy more time off work and do the things you like to do. I am getting the experience I want out of life right now. I am happy running my little corner of the darkweb and making profit simply by virtue of knowing the right people. My favourite line from the film Layercake words it better than I can: "The art of good business is being a good middleman." Being a good middleman is my business. My name? If you knew that I'd have a real big problem.
